snippet.title: Mixolumia Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Mixolumia introduces a fresh twist on block-clearing puzzlers. Scintillating visuals and entrancing music respond to your input and evolve as you progress. Gravity and the gem-shaped board enable you to set up chain reactions and earn high-scoring combos.

Learn more at https://www.mixolumia.com
